{
  "texts": [
    "The majority of comments, 287 out of 355, are written with a neutral, objective tone.",
    "Furthermore, there are 34 positively written comments (e.g., \"Answer is surprisingly good\") and 34 negatively written comments (e.g., \"The answer is quite bad\").",
    "We do not observe a strong sentiment in the free text comments as 81% of the comments have a neutral tone and there are as many positively as negatively written free text comments.",
    "We discuss the assessed capabilities of ChatGPT in natural science and engineering with regard to previous domain-specific studies.",
    "We further focus on possible implications for education and ethical use of ChatGPT in natural science and engineering."
  ]
}